&lt;p&gt;🌎 We&#39;re hiring a Senior AI Engineer to be our engineering presence on the ground in the US — someone who sits alongside our US Sales and Customer Success teams, builds fast, and turns a prospect&#39;s problem into a working demo while the deal is still live.&lt;/p&gt;
