&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;📍You&#39;ll work from our NYC Midtown office&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;~2 times per month, the rest of your time can be remote based in the following East Coast States: Pennsylvania, Rhode Island, New York, New Jersey, North Carolina, Virginia.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
